SPELL NAME  : Cleric muff
SPELL SYNTAX: Cmuff <on/off>
SPELL COST  : NONE
DESCRIPTION : Though much of the Cleric's power comes from his relationship
	      with his fellow guild members, there are times when the devote
	      Cleric will want to commune privately with Mitra. The Cleric
	      uses this power to choose when he or she wishes to open their
	      mind to their fellow Clerics or when they wish to commune
	      privately with Mitra.
